2
00:00:04.890 --> 00:00:06.810
Five and one; evens win.

3
00:00:13.530 --> 00:00:14.780
Wow!

4
00:00:15.430 --> 00:00:19.270
They say it all depends on
the roll of the dice...

5
00:00:20.660 --> 00:00:24.870
but luck's on your side, milord!
You're on a winning streak!

6
00:00:24.870 --> 00:00:25.960
Here.

7
00:00:29.390 --> 00:00:32.470
Take this for the sushi on the boat.

8
00:00:32.470 --> 00:00:35.840
Wow! This is more than I paid, mister!

9
00:00:36.450 --> 00:00:38.760
Don't worry. I'll win some more.

10
00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:42.060
Wowee!

11
00:00:42.060 --> 00:00:44.980
We only dropped by to take
shelter from the rain!

12
00:00:45.910 --> 00:00:49.400
If I stay with you, I'll never go hungry!

13
00:00:50.050 --> 00:00:53.030
Seriously! You're the savviest man in Wano!

14
00:00:56.890 --> 00:00:59.660
I think the sake will taste good tonight.

15
00:01:00.990 --> 00:01:03.200
Now, place your bets!

16
00:01:06.150 --> 00:01:07.040
Odds!

17
00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:11.960
Wow! You're not one to mess around, mister!

18
00:01:13.340 --> 00:01:15.600
We've got a bet on odds!

19
00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:27.440
All set.

20
00:01:32.940 --> 00:01:34.780
Here we go!

21
00:01:40.530 --> 00:01:42.040
Oh!

22
00:01:47.490 --> 00:01:49.000
No-Sword Style...

23
00:01:49.670 --> 00:01:52.130
Dragon Twister!

24
00:02:07.940 --> 00:02:11.060
Oh?! They were cheating!

25
00:02:11.860 --> 00:02:14.230
How lame.

26
00:02:17.890 --> 00:02:19.910
Guys! Get out here!

27
00:02:24.090 --> 00:02:27.910
At least your hospitality
doesn't seem to be lacking.

28
00:02:29.790 --> 00:02:31.630
Everyone! Get him!

29
00:02:42.790 --> 00:02:44.260
One-Sword Style...

30
00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:51.060
Dragon Quake!

31
00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:17.090
Whoa, wait a minute, mister!

32
00:03:17.390 --> 00:03:22.990
We live our lives on the cusp of
evens and odds, just as with good and evil.

33
00:03:22.990 --> 00:03:26.080
Let's put an end to this here!

34
00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:26.970
Okay?!

35
00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:34.650
Now, manager, there was
an objection to the last game.

36
00:03:36.820 --> 00:03:40.700
Damn! Just take it! Don't ever come back!

