OTOKO (MAN)?

398
00:28:58.380 --> 00:29:01.300
I'm just a girl named Otoko.

399
00:29:03.010 --> 00:29:06.470
Isn't it funny? Isn't it amusing?

400
00:29:15.100 --> 00:29:17.810
People always say it's easy to remember!

401
00:29:20.850 --> 00:29:23.490
Uh-huh! Yeah! I'm sure I won't forget!

402
00:29:23.490 --> 00:29:25.280
That's a great name!

403
00:29:26.240 --> 00:29:28.030
Totally!

404
00:29:30.310 --> 00:29:32.830
