Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!

484
00:33:30.990 --> 00:33:32.870
What a funny guy!

485
00:33:37.110 --> 00:33:38.630
Sir Luffy!

486
00:33:39.490 --> 00:33:42.080
Raizo! How did it go?!

487
00:33:42.080 --> 00:33:43.200
Sorry for the wait.

488
00:33:43.200 --> 00:33:48.490
I found the key to your seastone cuffs, but...

489
00:33:48.490 --> 00:33:50.360
it's under tight security.

490
00:33:50.360 --> 00:33:54.300
Not only is it guarded,
but it's in a seastone box!

491
00:33:55.300 --> 00:33:56.430
That said...

492
00:33:57.430 --> 00:34:01.220
I'll steal it at any cost.
Please give me a little more time.

493
00:34:01.220 --> 00:34:03.890
Okay! Got it!

494
00:34:07.800 --> 00:34:09.810
Alright!

495
00:34:28.600 --> 00:34:29.920
You again!

496
