506
00:34:53.930 --> 00:35:00.200
Luffy met this vicious, yet ill-fated,
pirate at the Sabaody Archipelago.

507
00:35:00.950 --> 00:35:08.410
He failed to take out the Straw Hat Pirates when he
raided the Sunny on her way to Fishman Island.

508
00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:14.250
After arriving on Fishman Island,
he continued in his wicked ways...

509
00:35:14.250 --> 00:35:17.800
