showed up and took him out.

513
00:35:34.950 --> 00:35:36.730
Caribou was then sent to Wano,

514
00:35:36.730 --> 00:35:42.500
and was forced into prison labor
at the mining camp in Udon.

515
00:35:47.690 --> 00:35:49.370
Oh, Boss...

516
