Millet dumplings for the needy!

518
00:35:57.000 --> 00:35:59.610
No way! Do your own work!

519
00:35:59.610 --> 00:36:01.760
You're so cruel!

520
00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:04.660
I heard about these seastone cuffs...

521
00:36:04.660 --> 00:36:09.770
They were made less potent
to allow prisoners to work still.

522
00:36:09.770 --> 00:36:12.850
Even so, I'm basically paralyzed...

523
00:36:12.850 --> 00:36:15.200
Push yourself harder!

524
00:36:15.200 --> 00:36:19.460
You're so harsh, Boss.

525
00:36:19.460 --> 00:36:22.570
If you give me dumplings,
I'll be your henchman.

526
00:36:22.570 --> 00:36:25.990
I've been here way longer than you,

527
00:36:25.990 --> 00:36:29.000
so I know more about the place.

528
00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:34.320
You'll do it, won't you, Boss?

529
00:36:36.710 --> 00:36:38.630
Shut up!

530
00:36:40.310 --> 00:36:44.590
You're planning to break out, right?

531
00:36:44.590 --> 00:36:47.060
Come on, let me in on it!

532
00:36:47.060 --> 00:36:48.140
Go away!

533
00:36:49.600 --> 00:36:51.890
No slacking off!

534
00:36:54.980 --> 00:36:58.650
Sakyo
Flower Capital

535
00:36:55.800 --> 00:36:58.650
A soba cook beat you?

536
00:36:58.650 --> 00:37:02.020
That's right! He was pretty tough!

537
00:37:02.020 --> 00:37:05.110
He overpowered the three of us.

538
00:37:05.890 --> 00:37:08.280
I'm gonna be busy today.

539
00:37:08.750 --> 00:37:12.960
I'm invited to Shogun Orochi's banquet...

540
00:37:13.380 --> 00:37:15.080
Contact Queen.

541
00:37:15.790 --> 00:37:19.840
Let's have him send an assassin.

542
00:37:19.840 --> 00:37:22.390
That's likely to cause an uproar...

543
00:37:22.390 --> 00:37:24.340
I don't care!

544
00:37:23.890 --> 00:37:24.340
Yes, sir!

545
00:37:29.500 --> 00:37:30.640
Shogun Orochi...

546
00:37:30.640 --> 00:37:34.390
the oiran is heading this way now.

547
00:37:35.200 --> 00:37:36.780
Excellent...

548
00:37:37.780 --> 00:37:39.480
Komurasaki...

549
00:37:42.490 --> 00:37:48.520
after today, you'll be mine!
